  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Personal Driver (Family)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong>:</p><ol><li>Provide dedicated driving services for the employer and family members on a daily basis, including commuting to and from work for the employer, daily travel arrangements for family members, and school & tutoring class drop-off and pick-up services for children.</li><li>Maintain the vehicle in a clean, tidy and well-maintained condition at all times.</li><li>Track and manage the vehicle’s maintenance and service schedules, ensure timely maintenance to keep the vehicle in good running order.</li><li>Strictly adhere to all traffic rules and regulations, and maintain a clean driving record with no violation history.</li><li>Assist the employer’s family with additional tasks as assigned from time to time (e.g., running errands for daily necessities).</li><li>Follow the employer’s instructions at all times; do not leave the post without permission, and do not use or drive the vehicle outside of authorized arrangements.</li><li>Able to communicate fluently in <strong>Mandarin</strong>.</li></ol><p><strong>Working Hours (General)</strong>:</p><p>5.5-day workweek with rotating shifts, which may include weekends and public holidays as required.<br /></p><p><strong>Vehicle Assigned</strong>: Alphard<br /><br /><br /></p>",
